gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Raptors 130, Wizards 122
gameRecap.excerpt: The Raptors defeated the Wizards, 130-122. Immanuel Quickley recorded a season-high 31 points, along with seven rebounds and 13 assists for the Raptors, while RJ Barrett added 22 points, eight rebounds and seven assists in the victory. Deni Avdija tallied 32 points, 10 rebounds, five assists and three blocks for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Raptors improve to 25-53 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 15-64.
